window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Amari Rivera's world has been turned upside down.</b></p> <p>After a shocking revelation about her husband Domonick's past, she flees, only to find herself trapped in a precarious situation. Navigating the looming threat of the Rossi crime family, Amari must confront her inner demons to survive.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Domonick is spiraling, betrayed by his own blood. As he races to save his wife, a deadly game of cat-and-mouse ensues, drawing in the entire Moody and Rivera organizations. Blood will be shed as old feuds resurface and new alliances are forged in the shadows.</p> <p>Caught in the crosshairs, Amari must find a way to escape before the Rossis' deadly plan is unleashed. Can she reclaim her life and her love, or will her fragile psyche be her ultimate undoing?</p> <p>In this gripping second installment, the stakes have never been higher as Amari fights for her freedom. With shocking twists and sizzling romance, what will be the fate of Domonick and Amari?</p>"; 
